cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.FL

This paper is about a graphical language for writing proof strategies, which is a topic in automated theorem proving and proof search. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Other relevant categories include cs.PL (Programming Languages), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory).
